<br>
Xanthurok was sad to hear the news that Asphyx was leaving Faydark. Asphyx told Xanthurok to follow in their fathers footsteps of becoming a Wizard. Xanthurok promised his elder brother he would do so. Asphyx left. The same boat his father was killed on, he rode. He traveled past the seafury cyclops. He made it safely to Freeport.<br>
<br>
In Freeport the city was alot bigger, and some turmoil was happening there. Asphyx didn't like the city and traveled west. Their he came upon a forest. It was alot like the forest of his back home. He traveled thru and found a hillside and was attacked by orcs. These Orcs had no chance. Asphyx killed them all, and moved on. He came to a city called HighKeep. There he met the Captain who was having problems with the goblins of Runnyeye. Asphyx took the offer to slay them. And when he was done, he went to Runnyeye and killed them. In the gorge he was attacked by Evil Eyes, thru the night they battled only to barely survive. As he left the gorge the king attacked, but was not a challenge. Asphyx killed over the years all over Antonica, and returned to Freeport.<br>
<br>
Back in Freeport he was told that a man named Sir Lucan was carrying out evil deeds. Asphyx did not care about this Lucan. But he gives a great sword as a reward, Asphyx didn't care about this sword. Only thing he cared about was either dead, or his brother back at Felwithe. Asphyx didn't know of love. Till one night. The mother of all Tunare came to Asphyx in a dream. She said one day he will find happiness and find a wife, and also warned him of the trouble on new lands and to the south. She blessed him and smiled down on him.<br>
<br>
One day while Asphyx was fighting south, he came across a man. He told him of a guild that could use him. Asphyx accepted and joined this new guild. Legion of Kings. He hunted with them for awhile, but they worried about little things, Asphyx had to move on. The Guild and Asphyx parted, and Asphyx traveled to a Iceland. The continent of Velious. Here is where he perfected his skills in combat, fighting alone, not knowing of friends.<br>
<br>
Back in Felwithe Xanthurok was learning more everyday. He began to fight the orcs. They was no match for his intense power. He too became bored with the orcs and moved on. He teleported all over the world exploring new places. Meeting new people. He still hasn't found his brother. His new home is in Highkeep where he fights the goblins and learns new magic. Xanthurok has surpassed his father in magic. Becoming a Great Wizard.<br>
<br>
The snow blowing hard in Velious is no place for a man to be alone. Asphyx stayed with the Tizmak in the caves thru the storm. The Tizmak told him storys of the Giants and of the Dragons, but mostly of the ones who call them selves Guardians in the city of Skyshrine. Asphyx thought it was a great idea. He left the Tizmaks and sneaked thru the giant city. He came to Skyshrine. This he thought was a great new experience. To learn more. To become a knight under them, but once he entered the city he was attacked. They fought hard and almost killed him. But thru the pain and blood Asphyx fought back. He slayed them all. He killed everything and the pool that use to be clear turned to blood. Asphyx left and teleported back to the freeport area.<br>
<br>
Back at freeport he encountered another strange person. Hello Friend he said. Asphyx looked at him strange. Would you like to join our fight against all evil? Asphyx accepted. The Guild Blood Circle has a new member. One who wont back down, One who wont quit, One who will become a Knight. Perhaps one day he will find a wife to mend his broken heart. And on that day... Vorphuix, Aspen, and Tunare will smile in heaven. Till then Asphyx is still in his everquest for Justice. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub5.ezboard.com/fbloodcirclefrm12.showPrevMessage?topicID=13.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub5.ezboard.com/fbloodcirclefrm12.showNextMessage?topicID=13.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub5.ezboard.com/fbloodcirclefrm12.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=13.topic&index=1><img src=http://www.tj3systems.com/bloodcircle/forumimages/bc_addrpy.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub5.ezboard.com/fbloodcirclefrm12.threadControl?topicID=13.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub5.ezboard.com/fbloodcirclefrm12.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=13.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub5.ezboard.com/fbloodcirclefrm12.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=13.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub5.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="bloodcirclebloodcirclegeneral">Bl